00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:33,160
is Yang...

279
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,830
Yang...

280
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:38,110
What Yang?

281
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:39,040
Gu Yong!

282
00:19:30,540 --> 00:19:32,980
[Tomb of Late Father, Zhuo Shanju,
by Son, Zhuo Lanjiang]

283
00:19:46,470 --> 00:19:47,040
Father.

284
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:50,470
It'll be two whole years
since you were gone.

285
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,190
I miss you.

286
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,710
There's a spy in Silver Rain Terrace.

287
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:02,040
This person is well-hidden.

288
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:03,680
He colluded with the Golden Water Sect

289
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:06,190
and is related to the Ripple Organization.

290
00:20:09,710 --> 00:20:10,520
Don't worry.

291
00:20:10,950 --> 00:20:12,400
I will catch that person.

292
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:14,040
I won't allow anyone

293
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,470
to destroy

294
00:20:15,830 --> 00:20:17,560
everything you've built, no matter what.

295
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:34,430
Father, do you still remember?

296
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:36,520
You always pushed me

297
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,040
to get married earlier.

298
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:39,710
You said I wouldn't be so stubborn

299
00:20:40,190 --> 00:20:41,350
after I got married.

300
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:43,830
I've met a girl I like.

301
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:44,950
One day,

302
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,350
I will bring her to visit you.

303
00:20:59,300 --> 00:21:02,920
[Maintaining the Peace]

304
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,560
Young Master.

305
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:07,830
Young Master!

306
00:21:09,430 --> 00:21:11,040
Young Master! Something terrible happened!

307
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:12,520
What's wrong?

308
00:21:12,560 --> 00:21:14,230
Gu Yong was killed in the county yamen.

309
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:19,590
Young Master.

310
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:22,830
This stamp pad was the item
that caused his death.

311
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,230
The needle is covered in deadly poison.

312
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,710
I guarded the court the whole night.

313
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:30,560
I even tested every dish Gu Yong ate

314
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:31,470
for poison.

315
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,350
I didn't expect them
to do something to the stamp pad.

316
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,350
The person who used the poison

317
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:39,110
must be familiar
with the workflow in the county yamen.

318
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,280
Check the background

319
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,710
of every officer
in the county yamen again.

320
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:44,000
Yes.

321
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,110
Now that Gu Yong is dead,

322
00:21:58,760 --> 00:21:59,800
we have no more clues.

323
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,880
What should we do next?

324
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:05,280
I wonder what Pan Yue is thinking now.

325
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:06,680
But he...

326
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,350
Miss Shangguan.

327
00:22:09,710 --> 00:22:10,640
Are you doing laundry?

328
00:22:10,710 --> 00:22:11,230
No.

329
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:13,430
Mr. Pan said he would no longer wear them

330
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:14,520
and asked me to throw them away.

331
00:22:18,310 --> 00:22:19,400
Thank you, Miss Shangguan.

332
00:22:42,560 --> 00:22:43,710
Miss Shangguan?

333
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:59,040
Mr. Pan, I have something to ask you.

334
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:00,280
What is it?

335
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:03,400
Was it you who saved me

336
00:23:04,590 --> 00:23:06,070
during the Lantern Festival?

337
00:23:13,470 --> 00:23:14,000
Yes.

338
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:16,520
Why didn't you tell me?

339
00:23:17,310 --> 00:23:18,280
Why should I tell you?

340
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:21,110
Your life was in danger
because you were investigating the case.

341
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,590
It was my duty to save you.

342
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,680
Why should I tell that to everyone?

343
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,040
I have one thing

344
00:23:39,590 --> 00:23:40,560
to tell you as well.

345
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:43,130
Two days later, I will ask Ze
to send something back

346
00:23:43,230 --> 00:23:44,470
to the capital.

347
00:23:44,950 --> 00:23:46,040
Return with him

348
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,470
so you have someone to take care of you.

349
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:48,470
I'm not going back.

350
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,160
I haven't found the truth
about the Ripple Organization.

351
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:51,350
- How can I...
- Shangguan Zhi.

352
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:55,680
You wanted to join the county yamen
to prove yourself.

353
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:56,920
I gave you an opportunity,

354
00:23:57,280 --> 00:23:58,310
and you did just that.

355
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:00,230
However, the Ripple Organization case

356
00:24:00,350 --> 00:24:01,590
will take half a month

357
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,880
to five years at most.

358
00:24:04,070 --> 00:24:04,800
Are you planning

359
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:06,350
to work in the county yamen forever?

360
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:09,520
If the river accident
were to happen again,

361
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:11,560
I would not be able
to guarantee your safety.

362
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,400
How can I explain it to your brother?

363
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,880
There's no need
to use my brother as an excuse.

364
00:24:23,640 --> 00:24:24,880
You chased me away

365
00:24:27,110 --> 00:24:28,680
because you were afraid
that I'd disturb you.

366
00:24:36,430 --> 00:24:37,880
Aren't you doing that right now?

367
00:24:49,350 --> 00:24:51,710
What? Is Miss Shangguan leaving?

368
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:59,430
Great. Silver Rain Terrace
will be waiting for you.

369
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,040
I heard what happened to Gu Yong.

370
00:25:03,590 --> 00:25:05,830
Mr. Pan, you couldn't even stop
a criminal in your own place.

371
00:25:06,070 --> 00:25:07,520
How can I let her stay here

372
00:25:07,590 --> 00:25:08,800
with peace of mind?

373
00:25:09,520 --> 00:25:10,110
If I take her away,

374
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:12,430
I'm sure you won't object to it, right?

375
00:25:17,710 --> 00:25:18,640
Of course, not.

376
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,190
With Silver Rain Terrace to protect her,

377
00:25:20,710 --> 00:25:22,000
I'm sure everything will be fine.

378
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:25,000
I can let go of this burden
and focus on the investigation.

379
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:25,950
Enough.

380
00:25:26,520 --> 00:25:27,950
I am a person and not an item.

381
00:25:28,590 --> 00:25:29,830
Have you thought about my feelings

382
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,760
when you are discussing
how you are going to get rid of me?

383
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:39,950
Young Master Zhuo,
thank you for your kindness,

384
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:42,590
but I will never go
to Silver Rain Terrace.

385
00:25:45,570 --> 00:25:46,410
As for you,

386
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,560
I'm sorry for burdening you

387
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:50,800
in the past.

388
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:54,000
However, I did not have
any intention of clinging to you.

389
00:25:55,710 --> 00:25:57,470
I will still investigate
the Ripple Organization,

390
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:01,590
but I won't
stay in your county yamen anymore.

391
00:26:18,230 --> 00:26:20,310
Young Lady, where are we going?

392
00:26:20,920 --> 00:26:21,830
Heyang is huge.

393
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:23,310
I'm sure we can find a place.

394
00:26:29,190 --> 00:26:29,880
Let's go.

395
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:37,300
[Heyang Magistrate's Office]

396
00:26:41,950 --> 00:26:42,560
Wait!

397
00:26:54,760 --> 00:26:55,230
Ling.

398
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,520
These are the fruits you like.

399
00:26:58,470 --> 00:27:00,680
I don't know when we will meet again.

400
00:27:01,190 --> 00:27:02,000
Take care.

401
00:27:50,580 --> 00:27:53,380
[Sunrise Garden]

402
00:28:05,560 --> 00:28:06,920
In the end,

403
00:28:08,110 --> 00:28:09,760
I've returned to this place again.

404
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:10,950
Are you sure you want to live here?

405
00:28:11,070 --> 00:28:12,230
This place has been vacant
for a long time.

406
00:28:12,470 --> 00:28:13,680
It's deserted.

407
00:28:14,470 --> 00:28:15,430
Why don't you reconsider

408
00:28:15,520 --> 00:28:16,400
and come to Silver Rain Terrace?

409
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,830
You can get anything
at Silver Rain Terrace.

410
00:28:17,950 --> 00:28:18,830
It won't be worse than this.

411
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:22,400
Thank you for helping me move today.

412
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,350
Since I've helped you move, you should
at least invite me for a drink.

413
00:28:28,170 --> 00:28:29,160
We do need to drink

414
00:28:30,560 --> 00:28:32,280
to celebrate my escape from prison

415
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:33,680
and the beginning of my new life.

416
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,310
Ling.

417
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:39,590
Prepare the liquor.

418
00:28:40,350 --> 00:28:41,430
Yes.

419
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:51,160
Do you know

420
00:28:51,230 --> 00:28:53,000
who the fattest person in this world is?

421
00:28:53,470 --> 00:28:55,590
The chancellor.
His stomach can hold a boat.

422
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,830
What about the fastest person?

423
00:28:59,590 --> 00:29:01,640
Cao Cao. Cao Cao will appear
as soon as he is mentioned.

424
00:29:01,830 --> 00:29:02,350
You lost again.

425
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:04,070
You know everything.

426
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,880
Again. I don't believe it.

427
00:29:12,430 --> 00:29:14,560
You've had enough.
You should drink another day.

428
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:17,110
What do you mean I've had enough?
Don't spoil my mood.

429
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,800
I must win against you.

430
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,310
People who have something on their minds

431
00:29:22,110 --> 00:29:22,950
can't win.

432
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,560
Do you know

433
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:33,800
who the most foolish person
in the world is?

434
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:49,070
The person
who fell into the same pit twice.

435
00:29:53,280 --> 00:29:54,560
I knew

436
00:29:56,190 --> 00:29:57,830
Pan Yue already had the princess.

437
00:30:00,430 --> 00:30:01,590
I also knew

438
00:30:02,710 --> 00:30:04,000
I had nothing.

439
00:30:07,310 --> 00:30:08,830
This name

440
00:30:10,950 --> 00:30:11,920
and this face

441
00:30:14,520 --> 00:30:15,430
aren't even mine.

442
00:30:17,470 --> 00:30:19,350
I was supposed to stay away from the pit.

443
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,560
But I fell into it

444
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:25,800
once again.

445
00:30:31,470 --> 00:30:33,560
That's not the saddest part.

446
00:30:35,230 --> 00:30:36,640
The saddest part

447
00:30:39,280 --> 00:30:41,470
is that I have no grounds to hate him

448
00:30:43,710 --> 00:30:45,400
or the right to love him.

449
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:49,230
I can't even tell him...

450
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:54,420
♪I wish I could be worthy of the thoughts♪

451
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:02,160
I can't even tell him

452
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:07,800
that I'm just a thief
living in someone else's shell.

453
00:31:09,190 --> 00:31:10,000
Tell me.

454
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:15,070
Am I a fool?

455
00:31:17,430 --> 00:31:19,110
You are not the only foolish person.

456
00:31:25,400 --> 00:31:26,520
I've known you for so long,

457
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,950
but I've never seen you so sad.

458
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:35,950
Pan Yue doesn't deserve you.

459
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:37,350
We should feel lucky

460
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:39,230
because we escaped the pit
before it was too late, right?

461
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:46,740
♪The depth of the past
is best left unexplored♪

462
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:47,880
Yes.

463
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:51,420
♪How many more falls
do I have to experience♪

464
00:31:51,820 --> 00:31:55,220
♪Before I can face love
and hatred with grace?♪

465
00:31:55,540 --> 00:31:58,900
♪Don't ask if it's a moment♪

466
00:31:58,940 --> 00:32:02,820
♪Of liberation or cowardice to let go♪

467
00:32:02,860 --> 00:32:07,420
♪Perhaps it's a misstep into your heart,
it's a hasty feeling♪

468
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:10,860
♪It's an unwillingness
to be just a passer-by with you♪

469
00:32:10,980 --> 00:32:15,060
♪Even if I were to die
after a few intense struggles♪

470
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:18,060
♪I would have lived a life worth living♪

471
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:22,620
♪If grasses and trees are sharp blades,
if mountains and waters are temples♪

472
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:25,740
♪It's good to be alive
even for a short moment♪

473
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:29,700
♪I wish I could be worthy of the thoughts♪

474
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:36,900
♪And I wish I could be worthy of the love♪

475
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:51,230
Shangguan Zhi, go and...

476
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:54,040
Young Master, it's me.

477
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:03,350
Young Master, Miss Shangguan
has returned to Sunrise Garden.

478
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:04,950
She did not go to Silver Rain Terrace.

479
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:08,350
However, Young Master Zhuo
also went to Sunrise Garden

480
00:33:08,430 --> 00:33:09,310
with Miss Shangguan.

481
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:12,110
From what I heard,
it seemed like they were drinking.

482
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:13,830
He was still there when I left.

483
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,400
Enough.

484
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:17,190
I asked you to protect her,

485
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:19,310
but I didn't ask you
to report all these to me.

486
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:21,800
Young Master, you are reluctant
to see Miss Shangguan go.

487
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:22,680
Why did you...

488
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:24,400
There's no reason. Go to sleep.

489
00:33:42,620 --> 00:33:45,460
[Heyang Magistrate's Office]

490
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:48,230
This stew has to be cooked longer.

491
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,920
Besides, vinegar should be added

492
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:52,680
to this dish before it is served.

493
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,350
- It's better with some vinegar.
- Let me try this.

494
00:33:55,430 --> 00:33:56,110
Right?

495
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:58,190
Sir.

496
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:01,800
Young Master.

497
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:04,470
These are the dishes made by the new cook.

498
00:34:04,520 --> 00:34:06,710
Try them. Come here.

499
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:22,320
It's too bland.

500
00:34:29,230 --> 00:34:29,800
It's too cold.

501
00:34:32,950 --> 00:34:33,670
It's too hard.

502
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,840
Enjoy. I don't have an appetite.

503
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:00,230
Are you

504
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:03,040
disappointed in me?

505
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:16,840
Young Master.

506
00:35:17,520 --> 00:35:18,120
Ze.

507
00:35:19,950 --> 00:35:22,120
Send this drawing to be fixed

508
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,560
and frame it again.

509
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:24,870
Yes, Young Master.

510
00:35:25,630 --> 00:35:26,320
Oh, Young Master.

511
00:35:26,560 --> 00:35:28,230
Gu Shan will be buried today.

512
00:36:16,600 --> 00:36:17,710
Sister!

513
00:36:20,100 --> 00:36:25,500
[Late Sister Gu Shan's Grave,
erected by Shuang]

514
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:34,660
♪In the stormy night♪

515
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:42,660
♪The dark hair of a charming woman
is reflected in the flame of a candle♪

516
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:48,100
♪Shrouded by year after year of memories♪

517
00:36:48,140 --> 00:36:51,820
♪I can do nothing
but feign indifference♪

518
00:36:54,950 --> 00:36:56,230
Sister!

519
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:02,460
♪Together and apart, just like quicksand♪

520
00:37:04,710 --> 00:37:05,670
Enough.

521
00:37:08,380 --> 00:37:10,420
♪Drift away in the clouds♪

522
00:37:10,460 --> 00:37:16,340
♪Driving away your dashing pretense♪

523
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:18,380
♪A drunken dream♪

524
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:24,000
♪A person I miss.
Of course I know if it's real♪

525
00:37:24,220 --> 00:37:28,420
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

526
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:35,900
♪I want to hold on to you
but I can only play dumb♪

527
00:37:52,950 --> 00:37:54,120
Why should I tell you?

528
00:37:54,470 --> 00:37:56,280
Your life was in danger
because you were investigating the case.

529
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:57,870
It was my duty to save you.

530
00:37:58,150 --> 00:37:59,760
Why should I tell that to everyone?

531
00:38:02,080 --> 00:38:04,360
If the river accident
were to happen again,

532
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:06,440
I would not be able
to guarantee your safety.

533
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:09,120
Do you know

534
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:11,470
who the most foolish person
in the world is?

535
00:38:12,910 --> 00:38:15,430
The person
who fell into the same pit twice.

536
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,910
I'm sorry for burdening you

537
00:38:18,040 --> 00:38:19,080
in the past.

538
00:38:19,390 --> 00:38:21,120
I will still investigate
the Ripple Organization,

539
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:23,420
but I won't
stay in your county yamen anymore.

540
00:38:23,420 --> 00:38:24,180
[Heyang Magistrate's Office]

541
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,670
The saddest part

542
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:30,040
is that I have no grounds to hate him

543
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:32,040
or the right to love him.

544
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:36,000
I can't even tell him.

545
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,390
Tell me.

546
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,040
Am I a fool?

547
00:38:44,540 --> 00:38:46,340
♪A drunken dream♪

548
00:38:46,420 --> 00:38:51,980
♪A person I miss.
Of course I know if it's real♪

549
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:56,340
♪Even if you're just by my side♪

